title: Sevyn With All Tree Of Us? Prolly
itunes:title: Sevyn With All Tree Of Us? Prolly
description:
TUE 8/16 - Sevyn Streeter stops by The Breakfast Club to discuss her new single "Prolly" featuring Gucci Mane, why she broke up with B.o.B., and whether or not she regrets giving hit songs away to bigger artists. Then a hot discussions starts after Sevyn & Charlamagne debate "cheating respectfully".
